data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Step inside this charming and spacious 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom home, spanning 2,484 square feet, nestled in the flourishing area of Davenport. Boasting a serene water view of Lake Saint Charles from its welcoming front door, this residence radiates warmth and tranquility. The open floor plan is a harmonious blend of comfort and modernity, bathed in natural light, with bespoke touches adorning every corner, ensuring a homely ambiance from the first step inside. The heart of the home lies in its combined living, dining, and kitchen area, designed to be an ideal space for hosting and entertaining. The kitchen is a culinary haven, featuring a granite-topped island, artisanal backsplash, sleek stainless steel appliances, and elegantly crown-molded cabinets. Upstairs, the master bedroom serves as a private retreat, complete with a dual-sink vanity and an expansive walk-in shower, located adjacent to a lofted area. The upper level also houses additional bedrooms and bathrooms, while an extra bedroom is conveniently situated on the first floor. Outdoor relaxation is epitomized by the covered lanai, perfect for unwinding. Hendon's location is a hidden gem, discreetly positioned behind Holly Hill Road, granting easy access to a multitude of amenities. Nearby, one finds the Advent Health Heart of Florida, the lush greens of Deer Creek and Southern Dunes Golf and Country Clubs, the vibrant Posner Park Shopping Center, the delightful Ovation Bistro, and the recreational wonders of Lake Eva Park and Aquatics Center. Moreover, the enchanting world of Walt Disney World, Animal Kingdom, ESPN World, and Epcot are just a stone's throw away, offering endless adventure and entertainment.
